Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Thatcher plans second term
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043x053
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Jun 1983
Mrs Thatcher hopes for a second term - eyes are now on Reagan to see if he will do the same. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less